        fixCode: '// ❌ Wrong — filters rows after grouping (slow)\nSELECT category, COUNT(*) AS total\nFROM products\nGROUP BY category\nHAVING in_stock = true;\n\n// ✅ Right — filter rows first, then group\nSELECT category, COUNT(*) AS total\nFROM products\nWHERE in_stock = true\nGROUP BY category;',
